IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User matthias.vogelgesang@gmail.com
UseIMAPS yes
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/mail/gmail/INBOX

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Labyrinth" "Tarsnap"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
